    "translation": "",
    "context": "_event.m.Otherbrother.getName() + \" suffers \" + injury.getNameOnly()"
  },
  {
    "key": "2bfe8f95b9e20a81e291e9ede18432e4b6e0b11b540c128f83c463ad2acd70e4",
    "original": "%houndmaster%, you are a houndmaster, handle this!",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "Text = \"%houndmaster%, you are a houndmaster, handle this!\""
  },
  {
    "key": "30cbe64b3d8ad5c60c4601f5b20b25ac05ee2b128bf23f0683d6bd461feeaa0a",
    "original": "A master of his craft, indeed.",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "Text = \"A master of his craft, indeed.\""
  },
  {
    "key": "5ba916722880e9f2fe0278249d34c9b18081ea49eba04dec5c22f696886360ec",
    "original": "During camp...",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "this.m.Title = \"During camp...\""
  },
  {
    "key": "1cd19ec0318ca68f2fae70c925fa1cae891cdccd49efb30a39a0e37595ba68a1",
    "original": "Let the hounds sort it out themselves.",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "Text = \"Let the hounds sort it out themselves.\""
  },
  {
    "key": "102302eeefdfb7574ff4f1ef673f6af16a6701a15bd1c40ea07f600415bfe838",
    "original": "Poor beast.",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "Text = \"Poor beast.\""
  },
  {
    "key": "c47bddd4f5bca164d92c9b50ac96924e814815c058a300800b29c3511a98a250",
    "original": "Poor beasts.",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "Text = \"Poor beasts.\""
  },
  {
    "key": "53af7804d85961e35833e91744ed3578a186c25d38a4c55cd813878f2d4ec42f",
    "original": "Someone separate the hounds!",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "Text = \"Someone separate the hounds!\""
  },
  {
    "key": "3a0d2f6d5f93f4cd23f67c14a9efed47ff9955c6ac22beee7c9354ee62ea0130",
    "original": "Such is their nature.",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "Text = \"Such is their nature.\""
  },
  {
    "key": "be02781e326ca560bb23c5c62ee02d2b473deacc2143158e2903124a8b91509f",
    "original": "They're ferocious beasts alright.",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "Text = \"They're ferocious beasts alright.\""
  },
  {
    "key": "8a0a68ff967e4a1664cfa8d9290ea8a360e814423a507ce69ffff70623a76c53",
    "original": "Well?",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "Text = \"Well?\""
  },
  {
    "key": "206a22ae79743f3b9862628939132ec211d951f223ce6d2a7b925ba56a76f2d9",
    "original": "You lose ",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "\"You lose \" + _event.m.Wardog1.getName()"
  },
  {
    "key": "206a22ae79743f3b9862628939132ec211d951f223ce6d2a7b925ba56a76f2d9",
    "original": "You lose ",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "\"You lose \" + _event.m.Wardog2.getName()"
  },
  {
    "key": "f6736c71ec86dcbf1dcf77d69334b0a33e8175d97485c10483b38b54fea1bc86",
    "original": "[img]gfx/ui/events/event_27.png[/img]The battle over, you have %randombrother% take a look at the wardogs. They growl as he approaches, but that's all they got to muster for the fight has been kicked out of them. He reports on a few broken teeth and they each got a bit of a limp, but they ain't lame. In time, they'll be good as new for fighting. Hopefully, just not fighting one another...",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "Text = \"[img]gfx/ui/events/event_27.png[/img]The battle over, you have %randombrother% take a look at the wardogs. They growl as he approaches, but that's all they got to muster for the fight has been kicked out of them. He reports on a few broken teeth and they each got a bit of a limp, but they ain't lame. In time, they'll be good as new for fighting. Hopefully, just not fighting one another...\""
  },
  {
    "key": "03bc07534d2b4bf96a6b1f0e2cd7864a70b0dea42ad248f7d67fd9dea0d93686",
    "original": "[img]gfx/ui/events/event_27.png[/img]You order %houndmaster% the houndmaster to do something. He nods and steps forward, calmly walking between the two fighting dogs. They bark and snap at each other, but both pause to eye the man coming in. One growls, but does in fact sit down. The other backs up, its tail wagging furiously, but there's still fire in its eyes. The houndmaster crouches down and pets them both on the head. One mutt lowers itself, and the other follows suit.\n\n The man slowly brings the dogs together, practically touching noses, and then whispers to them both. Slowly, but surely, the bestial energy leaves the dogs and their softened dispositions seem more fit for watching children than fighting in a mercenary band. The houndmaster gets back up and the dogs happily follow him. He nods.%SPEECH_ON%Just a small row between dogs, heh.%SPEECH_OFF%He walks off while the rest of the company looks on slackjawed, as if they'd just watched some kind of procession of druidic sorcery.",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "Text = \"[img]gfx/ui/events/event_27.png[/img]You order %houndmaster% the houndmaster to do something. He nods and steps forward, calmly walking between the two fighting dogs. They bark and snap at each other, but both pause to eye the man coming in. One growls, but does in fact sit down. The other backs up, its tail wagging furiously, but there's still fire in its eyes. The houndmaster crouches down and pets them both on the head. One mutt lowers itself, and the other follows suit.\\n\\n The man slowly brings the dogs together, practically touching noses, and then whispers to them both. Slowly, but surely, the bestial energy leaves the dogs and their softened dispositions seem more fit for watching children than fighting in a mercenary band. The houndmaster gets back up and the dogs happily follow him. He nods.%SPEECH_ON%Just a small row between dogs, heh.%SPEECH_OFF%He walks off while the rest of the company looks on slackjawed, as if they'd just watched some kind of procession of druidic sorcery.\""
  },
  {
    "key": "e938151d8b792082eb521e57ae27ec4bade4cb2e573629e1b00078aec233684f",
    "original": "[img]gfx/ui/events/event_34.png[/img]%otherbrother% manages to separate the two wardogs before they kill one another. Unfortunately, he paid a price heavy with bites and scratches. He'll survive, but you can't help but notice that he's very skittish and wary of the dogs now.",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "Text = \"[img]gfx/ui/events/event_34.png[/img]%otherbrother% manages to separate the two wardogs before they kill one another. Unfortunately, he paid a price heavy with bites and scratches. He'll survive, but you can't help but notice that he's very skittish and wary of the dogs now.\""
  },
  {
    "key": "342a0bf4372fe8dc3cbadb10423b88402501956375f275d461a932f85550b397",
    "original": "[img]gfx/ui/events/event_37.png[/img]A series of barks followed by muted growling interrupts your work. You leave your tent to see that the two wardogs, %randomwardog1% and %randomwardog2% are fighting. They've locked their jaws onto the nape of each other's necks. A few brothers try to intervene, but every time they do the wardogs briefly separate and snap at the humans as if to say this fight is between them and them only.",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "Text = \"[img]gfx/ui/events/event_37.png[/img]A series of barks followed by muted growling interrupts your work. You leave your tent to see that the two wardogs, %randomwardog1% and %randomwardog2% are fighting. They've locked their jaws onto the nape of each other's necks. A few brothers try to intervene, but every time they do the wardogs briefly separate and snap at the humans as if to say this fight is between them and them only.\""
  },
  {
    "key": "04be3a3bd44246bdc78c5d2533bf6d960eea3ba8a6e76dbcd8eca5b62c1675a5",
    "original": "[img]gfx/ui/events/event_37.png[/img]One wardog limps off from the melee, leaving behind a dead mutt. That the winner did not even eat or try to eat the loser shows all you need to know about these animals' namesake. You have %randombrother% take care of the survivor while a few other brothers bury the body of the departed.",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "Text = \"[img]gfx/ui/events/event_37.png[/img]One wardog limps off from the melee, leaving behind a dead mutt. That the winner did not even eat or try to eat the loser shows all you need to know about these animals' namesake. You have %randombrother% take care of the survivor while a few other brothers bury the body of the departed.\""
  },
  {
    "key": "5319f7f8cf3e6108e0a60e68f6a271fc9ef9cb236d874ec4e6d8fdb4ef6768be",
    "original": "[img]gfx/ui/events/event_37.png[/img]Unfortunately, both dogs passed away. They died with bloodied fur clenched in their jaws, each one sharing a sum of both victory and defeat. You have %randombrother% bury the bodies lest their smell attract even angrier beasts.",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "Text = \"[img]gfx/ui/events/event_37.png[/img]Unfortunately, both dogs passed away. They died with bloodied fur clenched in their jaws, each one sharing a sum of both victory and defeat. You have %randombrother% bury the bodies lest their smell attract even angrier beasts.\""
  },
  {
    "key": "a5951c92b2c8c26ae57202628464d08b7156b39da9e0d15b041d07a6a7ffea96",
    "original": "[img]gfx/ui/events/event_37.png[/img]You elect to stand back and let nature take its course. Once the dust settles, you step forward to see how everything shook out.",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "Text = \"[img]gfx/ui/events/event_37.png[/img]You elect to stand back and let nature take its course. Once the dust settles, you step forward to see how everything shook out.\""
  },
  {
    "key": "b165acc53db799c537492dd54c6222227270998c6d92f5de006b92456071f358",
    "original": "[img]gfx/ui/events/event_37.png[/img]You yell at %otherbrother% to separate the two wardogs. He takes up a long stick and lowers it into the furred and furious melee. The dogs yelp as the metal comes between them. One takes hold of the pole-handle and rips it forward, dragging the brother into the fray. Man and beast blur together as all three fight for their own survival, each taking turns at fighting off the other. As the dust settles, you take stock of who or what is still standing.",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "Text = \"[img]gfx/ui/events/event_37.png[/img]You yell at %otherbrother% to separate the two wardogs. He takes up a long stick and lowers it into the furred and furious melee. The dogs yelp as the metal comes between them. One takes hold of the pole-handle and rips it forward, dragging the brother into the fray. Man and beast blur together as all three fight for their own survival, each taking turns at fighting off the other. As the dust settles, you take stock of who or what is still standing.\""
  }
]